  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would punish them in a way that the rest of the population had to watch it to see what was being done to these people who disobeyed these orders, in order to make sure that they will feel that in order it should not happen to us, we may as well give it up.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the-- the normal consensus was that, sooner or later, if I-- if I hide something, they will find it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- they didn't even talk about the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But soon after, they started to send in the Jews that were living in the-- in the main quarters of the city, in the more affluent quarters, to the more-- to the slum areas of the-- of the city of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they officially designated the poorest area of Lodz, that this will be the area of the-- of a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they set the date, which I don't-- I'm sorry that I don't remember the exact date, but it was either the 1st or the 15th of April of 1940.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was the time that this ghetto will be sealed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by that time, every Jew living in the city of Lodz had to be moved into this area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And whoever will be caught outside this designated area will be shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So naturally, all the people, all the Jews living outside this area, started to move in with as-- as little or as much as they could barely take with them, not even knowing where they will live, in which house and which apartment.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
